  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (W-AR-05 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility package for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. This package embeds weakener W-AR-05: one validation result discusses a comparator dataset by name in its narrative but omits the required comparedAgainst link, and a second validation result references a comparator whose experimental conditions (cyclic fatigue loading at 5 Hz, N=50 000 cycles) do not match the declared COU (static monotonic compression-bending per ASTM F1717). The mismatch is stated explicitly in the validation narrative below. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed.",
